snippet.textDisplay:
I have a few (great!) things to say:
1) Thank you for introducing us to Jordan. WE LOVE HIM. I can speak for everyone when we say, we love him. ♥♥
2) It is so GREAT to see you again, Jaclyn, seemingly happier and full of joy and life again. We missed your smile, your laugh... your sass!
3) When you told the story about how he gave you time to heal, that sealed the deal - he is great man. Back to number 1... we love Jordan!
4) We miss you on Snapchat. I know you're probably sick of it, but we miss you.
5) The more genuine and real you are, the easier it is to relate to you... and this... this feels SO relatable.
